name: Noob-leyon
description:
The comment section is locked on this account because I'm being targeted by people.

I swear I didn't reference RossDraws arts.

Trained on 62 Images, 5 Repeats, 10 Epoch, 64 DIM, lr = 1e-5, cosine with restarts.

USE TRIGGER - eyelashes, lips for getting similar effects.

These 2 are necessary Triggers!!!!!

you might Wanna mix it with my other models to produce better results.

ConceptART, OldSamia etc.

To the fan bombers : I know you are gonna use it too :p
